{"tid":1006172,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"認真嘅感情係唔會輕易放低","createTime":"2019-02-02T18:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T09:33:42.000Z","uid":173326,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71561690904effc91556f36df9d1a3a25efd09bf","tid":1006172,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:06:31.000Z","msg":"仲掛住人咪認囉，不過要清楚你掛住嘅只係當日嘅佢，而嗰個人以後都唔會再返嚟，而家嘅佢只係個外貌似曾相識嘅陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你係想有段美好嘅愛情，咁你遲早都會放低ex，因為你日後會遇到更適合你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當你忘記同ex講過嘅一生一世嘅時候，恭喜你，你已經放低左ex(呢個情況往往都係因為你已經遇到一個第二個target <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n如果你只係想同ex一齊，唔好意思，你要接受自己以後都會一個人，每日沉淪係過去嘅美好，而且身邊朋友會不停叫你move甚至覺得你痴線/話你扮情聖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係當你發夢見到佢嘅時候，你可以問心無愧咁同佢講，你一直都好掛住佢，就好似當日講過嘅永遠只愛佢一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e1d6d814262e85384d954200acaa461cf3b1bc","tid":1006172,"uid":173326,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:41:58.000Z","msg":"明嘅可以揮下手圍下爐，成日俾人講到好似唔放低就有錯咁，好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9327f875f027b12a1ca3c3f657fee2ec5a2848de","tid":1006172,"uid":6111,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:52:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而家嘅佢只係個外貌似曾相識嘅陌生人</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fb285a4901aa7f71f5b16911f8cc97198b6bf4","tid":1006172,"uid":104138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:53:19.000Z","msg":"就係你唔肯放低過去既人，傷害左身邊等你愛你既人"},{"pid":"8725c01cc4fce59270db47424f6d617def47df5c","tid":1006172,"uid":220175,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T18:56:11.000Z","msg":"唔會輕易放低但總有一日都要放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sm